name: skeleton lover genesis
description:
GENESIS

november 5th 2021

i chewed my fingers to the
bone before i arrived at
your door.
i hope you don’t mind a 
skeleton as a non-binary boyfriend 
because i satiate 
my hunger with nicotine
and the thought that billionaires 
will end up six feet deep
just like me.
i know it ain’t 
all that healthy, but
hopefully you’ll accept me for 
me.
